# pyUIauto

[![PyPi version](https://badgen.net/pypi/v/pyuiauto/)](https://pypi.org/project/pyuiauto/)
[![PyPi license](https://badgen.net/pypi/license/pyuiauto/)](https://pypi.org/project/pyuiauto/)
